description.en:
Cloud9BSC is changing the way you interact with musical artists. Since the genesis of record labels, individual and group artists have felt the sting from overindulgent agents taking half or more of their hard earned money. We are here as a group to step in and decentralize music through NFT adoption, to change the way that fans interact with their favorite artists and help the independent artist grow within a new space that is not easily navigated.

Cloud9 is a token based on the Binance Smart Chain that offers BNB rewards and giveaways. Its ecosystem will offer an NFT marketplace and cross chain DEX options.
